  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-red-route.htm",
  "title": "Hermits Rest (Red) Route Shuttle Bus - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_828672\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2665965_828672\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481828\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_2665965_481828\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Hermits Rest (Red) Route Shuttle Bus</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5922611\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_854587\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_854587\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Map showing Hermit Road, indicated by a red line, and 9 scenic overlooks along the 7.5-mile road that follows the rim of Grand Canyon.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Hermit-Rd-S-Rim-Pocket_4.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Si te quedas en el autobús, el viaje de ida y vuelta dura 80 minutos.\"/>\n<figcaption>Along Hermit Road, the shuttle buses are great when you use them in conjunction with the Canyon Rim Trail. You can get off at one stop, enjoy a scenic walk along the rim, then get back on the bus at the next stop. If you just stay on the bus, the entire round trip takes 80 minutes. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_8085610\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_8085610\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Hermits Rest (Red) Route</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>This route provides transportation between <strong>Grand Canyon Village</strong> and <strong>Hermits Rest</strong> along a 7 mile road along the rim of the canyon with bus stops at 9 exceptional scenic overlooks.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_8027626\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_8027626\"><aside class=\"fact-check\">\n<h4>Note: Hermit Road is Closed to Private Vehicles Between March 1, and November 30</h4>\n<p><ul>\n<li>Hermit Road can only be accessed by the free Hermit Rest shuttle bus, commercial tour - or by bicycle - or on foot  </li>\n<li><em>Hermit Road is open to private vehicles (under 22 feet/6.7 m) only during December, January and February.  </em></li>\n</ul></p>\n</aside></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2665968\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2665968\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Red_bus_5785.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Shuttle bus passengers boarding at Hermits Rest. Grand Canyon beyond.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/Red_bus_5785.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Last stop on the Hermit Road (Red) Route, historic Hermits Rest </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h3>Hermits Rest (Red) Route</h3>\n<h3>Spring Schedule</h3>\n<p><strong>March 1, through May 22, 2026</strong><br/>\n80 minutes round trip (without getting off the bus)</p>\n<p><strong>First bus is at 8:00 am — last bus is one hour after sunset</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Every 15 minutes: 8:00 am to 10:30 am</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Every 8 minutes: 10:30am to one hour after sunset</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2665966\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2665966\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Hermit Rest Route - Need to Know</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Outbound buses stop at <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-road.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5899888,hermit-road.htm,11006|\">all nine overlooks.</a></strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Return trip buses stop only at these 4 stops:</strong><br/>\n<strong>Hermits Rest, Pima, Mohave, </strong>and <strong>Powell Points</strong> (see loop map below).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>The last outbound bus</strong> leaves the Village Transfer Station <strong>at sunset.</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>The last return bus</strong> sweeps one hour after sunset.<strong> </strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>The last return bus</strong> stops at <strong>all Hermit Road bus stops</strong> on the way back to the village.  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>During the busy seasons, the line can be long at the Hermit Road Transfer Station – you may have to wait in line for two to three buses. </strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>If you don't want to wait in the shuttle line, and are capable of a short, but strenuous hike on a paved footpath,</strong> <strong>walk 0.7 mi (1.1 km) up to Trailview Overlook, </strong>where you can board an outbound shuttle buse —or continue walking along the <strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/upload/RimTrail.pdf\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1910277|\">Canyon Rim Trail</a></strong> as far as Hermits Rest, 7.1 miles (11.4 km).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2665967\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2665967\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Hermit Road Route (red) shuttle bus loop map\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/red-loop-diagram.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2666219\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2666219\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Points of Interest</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/upload/RimTrailMap.pdf\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5861737|\">Canyon Rim Trail</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/trailview-overlook-hermit-road-red-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645072,trailview-overlook-hermit-road-red-route.htm,31100|\">Trailview Overlook</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/maricopa-point.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644859,maricopa-point.htm,31100|\">Maricopa Point</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/powell-point.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645066,powell-point.htm,31100|\">Powell Point and Memorial</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/hopi-point.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6648523,hopi-point.htm,31100|\">Hopi Point</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/mohave-point.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645070,mohave-point.htm,31100|\">Mohave Point </a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/the-abyss-hermit-road-red-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645054,the-abyss-hermit-road-red-route.htm,31100|\">The Abyss</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/monument-creek-vista-hermit-road-red-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645048,monument-creek-vista-hermit-road-red-route.htm,31100|\">Monument Creek Vista </a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Greenway Trail</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/pima-point.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645052,pima-point.htm,31100|\">Pima Point</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/hermits-rest.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645044,hermits-rest.htm,31100|\">Hermits Rest</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/hermit-trail.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6645042,hermit-trail.htm,31100|\">Hermit Trail</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-road.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5899888,/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-road.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\"> <em>View photos from the scenic overlooks along Hermit Road </em></a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6382458\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6382458\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>South Rim Shuttle Bus Route Map</h2>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6382308\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6382308\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Map showing South Rim Grand Canyon Village and Vicinity showing three shuttle bus routes that are in service during the spring. The 4 routes are indicated by blue, orange purple and red lines.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/South-Rim-Pocket-Map-3000-wide-copy-spring-2026.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n<figcaption>This spring, 3 shuttle bus routes are in service from March 1, through May 22, 2026. Kaibab Rim (Orange) Route, shown on the right, transports visitors to S. Kaibab Trailhead, outstanding scenic views at Yaki Point, and Yavapai Geology Museum. Village (Blue) Route, center, connects the Visitor Center with lodges, campgrounds, Backcountry Information Center, and Market Plaza (general store and post office). Hermits Rest (Red) Route, on the left) follows a scenic road for exceptional canyon views. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5967817\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5967817\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Inclement Weather Operations on Hermit Road </span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>During <strong>summer thunderstorms </strong>or other inclement weather, <strong>shuttle bus service will be suspended on Hermit Road.</strong> </li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Visitors will not be transported via shuttle bus from the Village Route Transfer Station, westward to viewpoints along Hermit Road.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>However, shuttle bus drivers along this route will do all they can to either shuttle visitors along Hermit Road east to the Transfer or become standing shelters out along the route.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>When service is suspended due to inclement weather, shuttle buses with additional capacity will stop anywhere along the Hermit Road it is safe to do so, and pick up visitors. </li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>More detailed information about <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lightning-danger.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5260436,lightning-danger.htm,11006|\">Lightning Danger</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6380765\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6380765\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Shuttle Bus Route List</span></h2>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1914943,/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Shuttle Bus Home Page</a><br/>\n</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/village-blue-route.htm\">Village (Blue) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/kaibab-orange-route.htm\">Kaibab Rim (Orange) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hiker-express-shuttle.htm\">Hikers' Express Shuttle</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-red-route.htm\">Hermit Road (Red) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"> </span>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/tusayan-route-purple.htm\">Tusayan Park &amp; Ride (Purple) Route</a><strong><font color=\"#660099\"> </font><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Not in Service </span><span style=\"color:#339900;\">- Summer 2026 Only</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2666222\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2666222\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p><em><strong>When walking or cycling at the Grand Canyon, make sure to take your time and carry food and water with you. The South Rim of Grand Canyon averages 7,000 feet / 2,134 meters above sea level. Visitors with respiratory or heart problems may experience difficulties. Exercising at this elevation can be strenuous.</strong></em><font color=\"#c0392b\"><b><i></i></b></font></p>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 28, 2026</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
